title: Ep. - 501 - NAOMIE OLINDO AND LEVA BONAPARTE FROM SOUTHERN CHARM
description:
Noamie Olindo and Leva Bonaparte from Bravo’s Southern Charm discuss the new season, how Leva weathered viewer reactions last season, and how Naomie felt about coming back to the show after a breakup.
